Package: libvarnam3
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Priority: standard
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Description: Varnam 3 shared library
 Varnam is a cross platform predictive transliterator
 for Indian languages. It provides a set of APIs enabling
 other programs to use transliteration, reverse transliteration
 and learn. Programs that link with the Varnam library can have
 Indian language input in their applications.

Package: libvarnam3-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libvarnam3 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}, libc6-dev
Multi-Arch: same
Description: Varnam 3 development files
 Varnam is a cross platform predictive transliterator
 for Indian languages. It provides a set of APIs enabling
 other programs to use transliteration, reverse transliteration
 and learn. Programs that link with the Varnam library can have
 Indian language input in their applications.
 .
 This package contains the development files (headers, static libraries)
